keting purposes to be posted on designated spaces in Student Center pending approval by Building Management.  Items that do not meet said criteria or that may be perceived as distasteful in language or appearance will not be posted.  All unauthorized postings will be taken down.    Posting Criteria         Table Reservation      All reservations will be made through the Office of Meetings & Conferences. This policy is established by the management of the UIC Student Centers to ensure the fair and equitable allotment of table spaces in the Student Centers. Table assignment is designed to allow for organizations and service providers to offer their information to the UIC campus community in a manner that is professional and respectful. This policy also is designed to ensure that UIC campus community members are not disrupted in their daily activities by organizations or persons who represent activities or services of which they have no interest. Use the link below to view full policy.    Table Policy         Other Building Policies          About Us    Back to main content           Contact Us     Feedback + Suggestions    Subscribe      Hours & Locations    Policies     Lounge Policy Information    Postings Criteria    Table Policy    Other Building policies      Staff Directory                  UIC Logo        Student Centers         Quick Links    Staff Directory    Student Employment    Feedback      Resources    Lockers Info and Policy    Bicycle Repair    Donation Bins      Tools    Building Directory    BM Reports    Operations Reports        BUTTON    Policies    Sustainability    Hours & Locations         Contact   scenters@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 